<td class="fn summary" style="">Irving Kristol</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="">School/tradition</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="/wiki/Neoconservatism_(United_States)" title="Neoconservatism (United States)" class="mw-redirect">American neoconservatism</a></td>
